    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bento Blocks</strong> 是一款 <strong>温馨治愈系解谜游戏</strong>，你需要 <strong>切割</strong>食材，并将它们整齐地放入便当盒中，同时尽量 <strong>减少切割次数</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/efd61bfebca7b75ffd664eb2ae93217f.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=419 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/efd61bfebca7b75ffd664eb2ae93217f.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/fcdd5a341115536f50d376cc98b7d92b.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/fcdd5a341115536f50d376cc98b7d92b.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>180+ 手工设计关卡</strong> 中发挥你的 <strong>料理创造力</strong>。每一关都有独特的小巧思和令人满足的解法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/c946e3bf58e1a09f81eb554d81560468.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=351 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/c946e3bf58e1a09f81eb554d81560468.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/b0677a63db1aa49c3fdea3030cd14b0f.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/b0677a63db1aa49c3fdea3030cd14b0f.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>按你喜欢的方式游玩！</strong> 在轻柔的音乐、小巧的关卡挑战和舒缓的画面中放松下来。 无压力、无计时——完全 <strong>按照自己的节奏</strong> 体验游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/eb0a1fc4be8e161386a69290a1bdc151.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=351 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/eb0a1fc4be8e161386a69290a1bdc151.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/94268ca68b42543969beaf5b8cabef86.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/94268ca68b42543969beaf5b8cabef86.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切得越少，你的食谱就能获得越多 <strong>星星</strong>…… 不过事情可能没有看上去那么 <strong>简单</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/59bab3857df03f2fda4c5020d13fbe45.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=351 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/59bab3857df03f2fda4c5020d13fbe45.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将美味食材装进各种 <strong>独特的便当盒</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切割次数越少，获得的 <strong>星星</strong> 越多</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩 <strong>180+ 手工打造的谜题</strong>，并在过程中解锁新的场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>现场录制的音乐</strong> 与 <strong>手绘艺术风格</strong> 中放松身心</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无压力、无计时</strong> —— 完全 <strong>自由节奏</strong> 地游玩</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/6e546e0f36cae59f67bfeb5ca8e5ad6e.poster.avif?t=1771473660\" width=1170 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311670/extras/6e546e0f36cae59f67bfeb5ca8e5ad6e.webm?t=1771473660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>感谢阅读！</i></strong><i>欢迎将游戏加入 <strong>愿望单</strong> 支持我们，并加入我们 <strong>温馨的 Discord</strong> <strong>社群</strong>！</i></p>",
